Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.67,0:01:40.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人类因人口膨胀而向宇宙移民已过了半个世纪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.26,0:01:43.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,地球周围漂浮着巨大的人工都市
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.71,0:01:45.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,作为人类的“第二故乡”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.37,0:01:52.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人们就在这里出生、成长、生儿育女\N并走向死亡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.59,0:02:00.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宇宙世纪0079年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.91,0:02:03.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,离地球最远的宇宙都市SIDE 3
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.49,0:02:05.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以ZION公国之名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.57,0:02:08.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,向地球联邦政府发起了独立战争
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.13,0:02:11.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在开始一个月的战斗里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.35,0:02:16.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,ZION公国和地球联邦军有半数以上的人口死去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.23,0:02:23.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人们对于自己的行为产生了恐惧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.93,0:02:33.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,‘核心战斗机逃脱命令’
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.43,0:02:57.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雪拉，病人的情况如何？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.66,0:02:59.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们一切正常
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.33,0:03:00.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,107号室正常！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.13,0:03:02.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.53,0:03:03.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老婆婆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.57,0:03:05.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请再忍耐一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.04,0:03:13.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好吗？大家好吗！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.46,0:03:15.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哈罗，静一点好吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.38,0:03:18.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老公公，来吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.51,0:03:20.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,芙劳·波，这里一切正常
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.00,0:03:21.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.92,0:03:26.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各位，若有事的话请告诉我吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.39,0:03:29.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对了，引擎有少许故障
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.13,0:03:33.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,难怪速度有百分之八的差距出现
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.16,0:03:37.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以再减百分之十二冲力来计算
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.70,0:03:39.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.04,0:03:44.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我看要进入卫星轨道有很大困难
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.17,0:03:48.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,应该可以和那边线路接通的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.78,0:03:53.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,弹射线的坚程度如何...？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.65,0:03:54.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这不必担心了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.92,0:03:57.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,弹射线本来是给GUNDAM用的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.92,0:03:58.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以核战机应该没问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.19,0:03:59.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.72,0:04:00.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎可以？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.96,0:04:02.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们是军人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.19,0:04:04.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有责任去保护百姓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.13,0:04:07.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.53,0:04:10.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但如果母舰放下难民
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.93,0:04:13.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,便可以回卫星轨道等候命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.04,0:04:16.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这里是ZION军的占领区
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.77,0:04:18.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎可就此放下他们呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.61,0:04:19.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,放难民在这里？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.71,0:04:21.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.31,0:04:23.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,队长的意思是要周围逃避吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.41,0:04:24.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我没有这样想过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.05,0:04:27.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我有说错吗？你要知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.75,0:04:29.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,粮食怎样？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.99,0:04:31.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,母舰上有近百人是不能作战的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.99,0:04:33.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,凯！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.39,0:04:35.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,刚才这位年轻人说的没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.79,0:04:38.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们这班人都是被联邦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.86,0:04:40.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,强迫往宇宙移民
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.06,0:04:43.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,经过千辛万苦才来到地球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.63,0:04:44.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,却不可着陆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.93,0:04:47.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是死不瞑目
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.54,0:04:49.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们大家的心情也和我相同吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.61,0:04:54.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我现在有个好办法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.14,0:04:57.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们可以用母舰的弹射系统
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.35,0:04:58.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,将核战机飞弹出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.49,0:04:59.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.72,0:05:01.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,当飞离敌人进入弹道轨道后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.38,0:05:03.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,便可以和联邦军联络了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.42,0:05:05.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他说的可能性很大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.39,0:05:07.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也计算过了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.92,0:05:10.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没错！只要将弹射线
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.49,0:05:12.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接入主要引擎的蒸气管内就可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.53,0:05:13.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是没问题的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.76,0:05:15.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.80,0:05:18.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隼人，米莱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.57,0:05:20.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那些难民发生了骚乱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.67,0:05:21.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请立即来吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.84,0:05:25.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我看大家一直和敌人比耐性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.71,0:05:26.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,根本就没用！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.18,0:05:29.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不如照提议试试
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.28,0:05:31.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,问题是杜林线的接驳是否可行？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.98,0:05:33.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算成功
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.82,0:05:36.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又有谁可抵抗发射的反冲击力呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.99,0:05:39.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是由我提案的，就让我去做吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.42,0:05:40.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即使失败也有我做牺牲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.89,0:05:41.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆罗！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.96,0:05:43.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是吗？真有胆识呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.83,0:05:45.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今次的事亦未必是一定失败
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.13,0:05:49.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,布莱特队长，快着手改装弹射器吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.47,0:05:50.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.67,0:05:53.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你认为如何，李中尉？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.54,0:05:57.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,当然是和参谋本部联络为首要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.18,0:06:08.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所有GUNDAM数据送来了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.45,0:06:10.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是！收集到的都送来了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.69,0:06:12.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真叫人吃惊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.76,0:06:15.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,单从外表观察推算出来的性能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.59,0:06:18.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已和我们的机动战士有天渊之别
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.93,0:06:21.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果还收集到内部结构就好了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.83,0:06:26.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,夏亚！你竟然对着这种机动战士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.27,0:06:27.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还可追迹了二日的时间？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.07,0:06:31.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡尔玛，我也费了很大的气力呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.21,0:06:32.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这不难明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.71,0:06:35.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,唔，我们不可再花时间了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.24,0:06:38.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以在15分钟内就改好吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.55,0:06:40.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这不太难
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.55,0:06:42.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要将主引擎的动力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.55,0:06:43.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蒸气管接入去就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.72,0:06:45.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆罗，快些
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.62,0:06:46.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,先吃点东西吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.96,0:06:48.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别吃太多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.26,0:06:49.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是！我在吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.54,0:06:50.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你听着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.50,0:06:50.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.09,0:06:53.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最初的30秒是十分痛苦的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.63,0:06:56.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,糟了！那些难民发生暴动了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.43,0:06:57.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,暴动？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.83,0:06:58.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.10,0:07:02.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那班老人将小琪他们捉去做人质
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.34,0:07:04.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要求White Base降落到地面呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.51,0:07:07.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别再吃了，会呕的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.92,0:07:08.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.81,0:07:09.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟着...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.91,0:07:10.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.11,0:07:13.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,芙劳·波认为小琪他们既幼小又可怜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.38,0:07:15.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已经自愿成为人质了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.12,0:07:19.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在核战机内有多少驾驶时间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.46,0:07:22.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有模拟的18小时...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.16,0:07:24.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,训练35小时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.39,0:07:25.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,实战2小时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.80,0:07:27.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原来你的经验是那么浅的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.80,0:07:30.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没办法了，那么只有加油吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.17,0:07:32.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.74,0:07:33.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不担心的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.10,0:07:35.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.20,0:07:37.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你最好的朋友芙劳·波被捉去做人质
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.94,0:07:39.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你知道一点也不担心吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.84,0:07:42.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隼人，这里有队长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.65,0:07:43.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,米莱、雪拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.18,0:07:45.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,良也在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.31,0:07:48.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我认为有他们处理一定没问题的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.28,0:07:51.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我现在只可做自己能力范围内的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.99,0:07:53.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆罗说得没错！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.19,0:07:55.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要去发射部份了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.99,0:07:58.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜托你！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.29,0:08:00.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你出去后要有心理准备
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.60,0:08:02.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,ZION一定会追踪而来的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.43,0:08:05.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.14,0:08:08.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在幸灾乐祸吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.57,0:08:10.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你干吗在大发脾气？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.11,0:08:12.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不过想忠告一下你便是了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.91,0:08:14.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,凯！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.38,0:08:16.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知！我是个没出息的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.58,0:08:18.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的说话根本不值得你动怒啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.91,0:08:20.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.92,0:08:23.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你已经不是小孩子了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.72,0:08:26.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的说话要有分寸呢！
