Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.30,0:09:11.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快！给我联络杜力中尉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.30,0:09:12.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,派小型战机过来接我！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.84,0:09:14.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,夏亚，这是什么意思？
