Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.74,0:09:58.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们想跳出包围网
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.21,0:09:59.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然后和联邦军联络呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.95,0:10:02.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,基地上空已布满粒子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.82,0:10:04.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以他们不能使用雷达的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.32,0:10:05.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在该怎办呢？夏亚
