Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.66,0:10:07.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在还赶得及！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.66,0:10:10.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,会在2分钟后截到它！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.36,0:10:10.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.46,0:10:11.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,夏亚！
