Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.22,0:10:43.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就不应捉来人质
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.93,0:10:52.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家收回手枪...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.37,0:10:53.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,收回手枪！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.70,0:10:58.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果我可回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.77,0:11:00.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想见见我的孙儿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.81,0:11:05.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也只想看看小时候的故乡...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.41,0:11:08.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我丈夫还未死，我想再见他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.19,0:11:11.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我没说不降落地球
