Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.19,0:11:18.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还有多久才可降落地面？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.50,0:11:22.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然一切工作由你们负责
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.33,0:11:25.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是我们为了平等地交涉
