Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.04,0:13:10.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,勉强可以看到的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.57,0:13:11.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要试试吗？队长！
