Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.91,0:16:34.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没问题的，只要用自然降落法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.51,0:16:35.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就会有1分钟停留在空中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.15,0:16:37.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的话一定可以做得到的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.61,0:16:38.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你只是说当然可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.15,0:16:41.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这么困难的事我没信心做得到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.38,0:16:42.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不是要生存下去吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.92,0:16:44.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆罗，快回White Base吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.15,0:16:46.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快回来！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.79,0:16:49.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好吧！没法了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.56,0:16:52.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,攻击，开始！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.61,0:17:06.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打开母舰特别门，快！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.48,0:17:14.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,准备降落，完成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.28,0:17:16.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我来了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.31,0:17:39.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,改变操纵线路...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.01,0:17:41.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是，雪拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.04,0:17:42.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我...可以做到吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.95,0:17:43.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆罗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.18,0:17:46.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在是没有人有信心才会去做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.42,0:17:49.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过阿姆罗，你是有才能的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.45,0:17:50.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要有自信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.69,0:17:52.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要打开特别门了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.70,0:18:05.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有机动战士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.97,0:18:07.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敌人机动战士出来了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.04,0:18:09.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我用ZAKU去应战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.07,0:18:11.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,将舰载机升到敌舰上空！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.83,0:18:12.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.15,0:18:20.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,ZAKU下来了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.42,0:18:21.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是夏亚！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.38,0:18:22.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么？夏亚？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.82,0:18:27.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我出发了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.19,0:18:31.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,落地面前1分20秒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.16,0:18:33.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定要打倒他！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.40,0:18:42.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这班家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.24,0:18:47.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,夏亚呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.69,0:19:00.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在地球内用自然降落法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.92,0:19:03.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是一般人可以做得到的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.49,0:19:07.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,气死人！GUNDAM竟在前面阻住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.43,0:19:09.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你...你们干什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.77,0:19:12.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等...等一等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.97,0:19:14.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,做什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.27,0:19:16.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们又想做什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.51,0:19:18.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,似乎是不能降落了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.74,0:19:20.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请让我们下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.71,0:19:21.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我求求你...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.14,0:19:23.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.25,0:19:25.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不用担心，先回房去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.65,0:19:28.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对了，请先回去吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.93,0:19:30.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂！干什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.15,0:19:33.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,无论如何我们是不会走的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.52,0:19:35.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,除非能让我们下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.44,0:19:48.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊！激光枪的能源没有了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.71,0:19:54.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不成，阿姆罗 先撤退吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.08,0:19:56.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被近距离击中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.88,0:19:58.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,装甲不一定支持得住的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.11,0:20:00.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但...但是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.18,0:20:02.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用火力掩护你吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.72,0:20:04.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小心炮弹！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.45,0:20:08.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.88,0:20:33.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这木马...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.28,0:20:34.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,夏亚！听到吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.55,0:20:35.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡尔玛！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.68,0:20:37.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我看你对联邦的机动战士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.49,0:20:41.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有必要再重新估计再定作战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.82,0:20:43.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.29,0:20:46.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在由计算机的推算所得
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.23,0:20:49.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敌机动战士是以战斗机为中心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.07,0:20:52.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以自由变换形式的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.20,0:20:53.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多用途机动战士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.53,0:20:53.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.07,0:20:57.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊！这岂不是说我一直所见的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.87,0:21:01.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是白色机动战士的部份威力？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.24,0:21:07.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那以后怎样应付呢？卡尔玛！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.68,0:21:08.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,先回来吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.75,0:21:09.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一起研究！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.59,0:21:14.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.50,0:21:23.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别理他们，阿姆罗！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.20,0:21:25.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,辛苦你了，阿姆罗！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.30,0:21:26.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要杯茶吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:27.35,0:21:27.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谢谢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.54,0:21:29.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这位小朋友..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.94,0:21:32.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又或者是在这里的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.41,0:21:33.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,都尽了力去战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.91,0:21:35.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这点我是体会的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.94,0:21:39.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是我们都老了..无能为力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.05,0:21:41.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只想回地球去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.02,0:21:43.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这点我是明白的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.72,0:21:45.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不如就让我们就在此地离舰吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.99,0:21:47.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还差一些
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.46,0:21:48.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就可进入联邦军的领地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.06,0:21:50.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么你们不再耐心一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.19,0:21:54.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但你可以保证我们的生命吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.76,0:21:57.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只希望我的儿子可以平安！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:58.17,0:22:01.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是只要一点时间就可降落吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:01.67,0:22:04.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们只会为自己设想的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:04.97,0:22:07.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你又怎会了解我们的心情呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:07.21,0:22:08.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那我问你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:09.08,0:22:11.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是否只为了自己而去战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.28,0:22:13.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也是为了大家才去拚命战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:13.95,0:22:16.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在不想再做下去了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:16.72,0:22:17.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆罗！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:18.55,0:22:20.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,先喝杯茶吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:21.86,0:22:24.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请你将芙劳·波和那班小孩送回来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:26.16,0:22:28.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们都全靠你了！小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:36.77,0:22:39.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆罗，你没事吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:41.31,0:22:42.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,横过山脉吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:43.27,0:22:43.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:43.75,0:22:45.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只好以山脉作屏障
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:45.21,0:22:46.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,正向着海面进发
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:47.08,0:22:49.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只好这样！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:19.42,0:23:22.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为了让难民降落而停战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:23.29,0:23:27.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是趁这空隙却已经在为下一场战斗布阵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:27.84,0:23:31.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而佩露西亚母子在他们所要归去的大地上\N所看到的是……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:32.69,0:23:33.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,机动战士GUNDAM
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:34.31,0:23:36.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下一集 ‘荒野是战场’
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:37.29,0:23:40.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你能够存活下去吗？

